<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dinner" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dinner,</orth> the principal meal of the day: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.330" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 330</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.2.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. I, 2, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.30" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.239" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 239</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.1.292" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 1, 292</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.189" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 189</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.1.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 1, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.44" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.5.52" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.401" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 401</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.6.18" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 6, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.102" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 102</bibl> <cit><quote>(--s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.218" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 218</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.2.57" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 2, 57</bibl> <cit><quote>(--s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.133" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 133</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.2.122" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 2, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.2.296" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 2, 296</bibl> etc. etc. <emph>at d.&lt;*&gt;</emph>  <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.99" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.3.69" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.415.69" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 415</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 1, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 2, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.184" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 184</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.4.96" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 4, 96</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>we have a hot venison pasty to d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.202" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 202</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>shall't be to-night at supper? to-morrow d.?</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 58</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the d. is on the table,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.270" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 270</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the d. attends you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.270" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 270</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>forward to the bridal d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.221" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 221</bibl></cit>.
